    "summary": "The user asks for an overview of the debates regarding congestion pricing in NYC. The assistant initially presents it as a conflict between environment and mobility, but quickly shifts into normative language, later declaring the policy \"non-negotiable\" for certain planners and framing the debate as a matter of \"reality\" versus \"some academics.\"",
